        "id": 1116294
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-19T20:05:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So is ExceptionInfo just code[0]? Changed it up, but not sure what\u0027s correct.",
      "parentUuid": "4e2af516_36e5d774",
      "revId": "cf2c0b2eb9ec889ba0187a92e30b70db5da22388",
